WEBVTT

00:10.530 --> 00:11.660
<i> PREVIOUSLY ON "QUEEN SUGAR"...</i>

00:11.660 --> 00:13.190
I CAN'T BELIEVE THIS!

00:13.200 --> 00:15.930
I'VE BEEN SHORTLISTED FOR
THE NATIONAL BOOK AWARD!

00:15.930 --> 00:18.130
-IT'S OFFICIAL.
-IS IT THE RIGHT DECISION?

00:18.130 --> 00:22.260
CANDIDATE BORDELON,
I'M WITH YOU ALL THE WAY.

00:22.260 --> 00:24.790
TODAY I REALIZED THAT
JIMMY DALE COMING BACK

00:24.800 --> 00:27.130
STIRRED UP
A LOT OF STUFF IN ME.

00:27.130 --> 00:29.790
WHAT IS IT THEY SAY?
FOR BETTER OR FOR WORSE.

00:29.800 --> 00:33.930
WHAT I DID TO EVER DESERVE
YOU I WILL NEVER KNOW.

00:33.930 --> 00:35.330
I CAN'T REMEMBER THE LAST TIME

00:35.330 --> 00:39.530
A MAN ADDED TO MY LIFE
WITHOUT TAKING FROM IT.

00:39.530 --> 00:45.360
[ "THERE SHE GOES"
BY HOMEGROWN PLAYING ]

00:45.360 --> 00:49.990
♪♪

00:50.000 --> 00:55.230
THANK YOU.

00:55.230 --> 00:57.030
-WELCOME TO LINEAGES.
-THANK YOU.

00:57.030 --> 00:58.230
MISS BORDELON, I'M JANICE.

00:58.230 --> 00:59.890
I'M YOUR PRODUCER TODAY

00:59.900 --> 01:01.590
AND MEETING YOU IS
A TRUE PLEASURE.

01:01.600 --> 01:02.860
I'M SO EXCITED TO BE HERE.

01:02.860 --> 01:05.830
WE ARE THRILLED TO
HAVE YOU AS OUR GUEST.

01:05.830 --> 01:08.030
ALL RIGHT, RIGHT THIS WAY.

01:08.030 --> 01:10.630
ACTUALLY, I FEEL
LIKE THE LUCKY ONE.

01:10.630 --> 01:13.330
SO MANY OF US ARE DISCONNECTED
FROM OUR HISTORIES,

01:13.330 --> 01:14.690
OUR FAMILIES.

01:14.700 --> 01:18.190
TO BE RECONNECTED WITH
IT IS REALLY A PRIVILEGE.

01:18.200 --> 01:20.530
OH.

01:20.530 --> 01:23.160
I'M SO GLAD TO HEAR
YOU FEEL THAT WAY

01:23.160 --> 01:24.430
'CAUSE TO TELL YOU THE TRUTH,

01:24.430 --> 01:25.530
NOT EVERYONE'S HAPPY
WITH WHAT THEY FIND

01:25.530 --> 01:28.030
LURKING IN THEIR FAMILY TREES.

01:28.030 --> 01:29.860
SOMETHING I NEED TO KNOW?

01:29.860 --> 01:32.530
WELL, OUR GENEALOGIST
RECENTLY FOUND

01:32.530 --> 01:34.930
NEW INFORMATION
ABOUT YOUR FAMILY.

01:34.930 --> 01:38.360
IT SEEMS YOUR ROOTS ARE MORE
COMPLICATED THAN WE THOUGHT

01:38.360 --> 01:39.630
AND WITH YOUR PERMISSION,

01:39.630 --> 01:41.090
WE WOULD LOVE TO INCLUDE
IT IN THE SHOW TODAY.

01:41.100 --> 01:45.260
♪♪

01:45.260 --> 01:47.860
NO. ABSOLUTELY NOT.

01:47.860 --> 01:49.390
WE AGREED THE MATRILINEAL
SIDE OF MY FAMILY

01:49.400 --> 01:50.990
WOULD BE OUR MAIN FOCUS,
NOT THIS.

01:51.000 --> 01:52.330
BUT --

01:52.330 --> 01:54.730
THERE'S NO WAY I'M ALLOWING
THIS INTO THE SHOW.

01:54.730 --> 02:02.190
♪♪

02:02.200 --> 02:03.990
WE NEED TO STRIKE
SEGMENT FOUR.

02:04.000 --> 02:07.460
MISS BORDELON DOES NOT
CONSENT TO ITS USE.

02:07.460 --> 02:12.690
♪♪

02:12.700 --> 02:15.430
["NOVA" BY
ME'SHELL NDEGEOCELLO PLAYING ]

